WEBVTT

00:01.472 --> 00:05.476
Sous-titres:
www.sub-way.fr

00:05.727 --> 00:09.731
www.starwars-universe.com

00:10.761 --> 00:14.765
{\when surrounded by war,
one must eventually choose a side}

00:16.815 --> 00:18.665
<i>Republic forces in retreat.</i>

00:19.042 --> 00:22.125
<i>While rescuing General Aayla Secura
from certain defeat,</i>

00:22.250 --> 00:25.000
<i>Anakin Skywalker
has been seriously injured.</i>

00:25.125 --> 00:27.799
<i>After a narrow escape,
our heroes crashlanded</i>

00:27.924 --> 00:29.974
<i>on the remote world of Maridun.</i>

00:30.099 --> 00:32.671
<i>Stranded, and with no way
to contact the Republic,</i>

00:32.797 --> 00:36.264
<i>the Jedi receive medical aid
from the peaceful Lurmen colonists.</i>

00:36.389 --> 00:40.206
<i>But even on this tiny planet,
the war threatens to follow the Jedi.</i>

